Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========TEXT==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一直都被研美骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果相信他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们迟早也会跟他走上同一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次才终于感觉到自己的认知是多么的肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须绷紧神经才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽同学 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 发生了太多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有留下什么可怕的回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我相信有马同学一定会来救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之吗


Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是研美集团过去十年的企业报告

Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:36.88,OT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,500)\fs25\pos(77,117)}#08\N 倾注真心

Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只调查到这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是些形式上的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来进行单独调查比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用自己的管道试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不尽快找出深藏的敌人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽 出发吧鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所指示的物品也已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少由我来说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 因为这是我自己决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~啊 都湿掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为社团活动时间太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 蓝羽同学他们请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微...等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么煞风景的房间啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是契约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前一直都没有理会有马同学的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是将我自己单方面的认知强加于有马同学身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学自己是不得已才被卷进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后和我订下契约 大家相互帮忙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么 意思是说我死了之后能得到一大笔钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先放在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你以「总之就这样吧」的心情战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就这么让你信不过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订契约什么的果然太不通情理了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要维持和有马同学的关系 就只有这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是琉璃抱著请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分男人都会被秒杀的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能做那样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要有马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人不得安宁的家伙啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法了…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了什么而战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你以「总之就这样吧」的心情战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的需要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼瓦它…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就挂了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要修理啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望两位帮我找到作为修复材料的石头啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的石头是不行的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也不行啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是「倾注真心」的石头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那如同玻璃般脆弱的心将会一分为二的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是一团黏土…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 为什么我得这么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只剩3天可活了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让琉璃一个人去我的出生地镰仓怎么能让人放心的下啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我一个人去没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在镰仓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 「倾注真心」的石头是什么样的石头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是 男女之间恩恩爱爱产出的结晶啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我说的太高深了吗啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到那种石头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位必须手牵手才行啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不对劲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 只是很少见到你这么穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女仆们帮我想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪怪的…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次坐有轨电车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我一直都是坐专车的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把你牵扯进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 本来也是我自己说要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到那种石头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位必须手牵手才行啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车马上就要进入三号线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:34.77,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了您的安全 请站在黄线外候车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要一起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你正忙的时候打扰真是过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自哈佛毕业之后就再也没见过面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你会当官之类的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有更重要的使命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的话应该能成为国之栋梁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太抬举我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个…拜托你的那件事如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对研美集团出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会被抹杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我一句 别再插手这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是江之电吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.91,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江の电 起点是藤泽市终点是镰仓市的电车 全名江之岛电铁线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你又被拐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 是我只顾著东张西望了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 总之没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系了啦 我不会再左顾右盼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大佛是在那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本大佛殿好像就是在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…这个就是鬼瓦的兄弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是迟啊琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 很恩爱的亲嘴嘴了吗啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别喊那么大声 对裂缝会有影响的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经得到碎片了 这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人倾注真心的话石头应该会发光的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有好好牵在一起吗啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼瓦怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说石头在发光之前 手要一直牵著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…先去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和有马同学一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 特大碗金枪鱼叉烧面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不一起来还比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么一直这副表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 有什么话你就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不说我怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生什么的气？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于昨天订契约的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很讨厌吗 和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是讨厌就不会一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和恶石战斗的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问都不用问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之什么的 有马同学每一次每一次都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的总之不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是很不情愿的万般无奈的战斗著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很认真的想著要救人要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗 是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直让她感到不安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种细微的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.84,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想在这种店里吃一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是因为我没好好的传达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点又要被我破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙您款待了 真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我吃过的拉面里最好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你告诉我啊 我也一样 不和我说我怎么会知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是朋友…的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没发光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就这样观察一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 难得来这里 要一起走走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个矮小的有马？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在长的还真高大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候在镰仓住的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我读小学之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我刚懂事的时候 老爸就已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽同学应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学的资料 全都在镜手上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多 有马同学的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬过来之后 马上就交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然互相都不知道名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天过的都很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是嚣张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无法原谅 而使用了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都因为这种原因搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是…失去朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直起脊梁好好振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你自己能好好振作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会破坏你和重要的人之间的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…从那时起一点也没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里对有马来说是重要的地方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 带著你到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果到最后石头也没发光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候有见到过有马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在建设中的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这么多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直禁止游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为横须贺那边好像发生了什么事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在总算开放了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都舍不得离开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有马同学守护住了大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 得救的人还有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有马同学不来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝壳还是什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是别人给的卖剩货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常正好相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我先收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是总之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我接受你的「意志」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我一个人什么也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果和你在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才明白了破坏的力量也能用来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 琉璃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么啊 当然是那个了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行到哪步了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…到江之岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是有马的这个喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真吵啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么修好了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为修理了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心的石头呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过爱的结晶 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火热火热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受镰仓的约会了吗鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙骗了我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次虽然没有得到决定性的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于研美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要深加调查
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝羽财团搅和进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被奈特的话所摆布了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙会查出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候…

